{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016GthVaD8YAu52VLyrdFHbh","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27\n     2→\n     3→### State corruption fix (2026-03-27T13:48Z)\n     4→\n     5→Stories 16-5, 16-6, 16-7 were at `review` in sprint-state.json despite committed as done with proof documents. Fixed by restoring `done` status. Same root cause as previous session — ralph state reconciliation overwriting committed state.\n     6→\n     7→### 16-8-update-all-tests — create-story (2026-03-27T13:49Z)\n     8→\n     9→- Ambiguity in epic definition: Task 8 in tech-spec is terse (\"Update all tests\") with no specific ACs. Derived ACs from tech-spec testing strategy.\n    10→- Used legacy tag names (`cli-verifiable`) per instruction — `LEGACY_TIER_MAP` maps them to `test-provable` at parse time.\n    11→- Risk: Story may require zero code changes if previous stories already added all tests.\n    12→\n    13→## Token Report\n    14→- Total tool calls: 17\n    15→- By tool: Read: 7, Grep: 7, Glob: 3, Write: 1\n    16→- Files read: 9 unique, 10 total reads\n    17→- Redundant operations: None\n    18→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b3a82007-2654-437f-8d26-bde42ea858b0","uuid":"4d926747-3746-4037-97d0-df6eab275599","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:08:53.022Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27\n\n### State corruption fix (2026-03-27T13:48Z)\n\nStories 16-5, 16-6, 16-7 were at `review` in sprint-state.json despite committed as done with proof documents. Fixed by restoring `done` status. Same root cause as previous session — ralph state reconciliation overwriting committed state.\n\n### 16-8-update-all-tests — create-story (2026-03-27T13:49Z)\n\n- Ambiguity in epic definition: Task 8 in tech-spec is terse (\"Update all tests\") with no specific ACs. Derived ACs from tech-spec testing strategy.\n- Used legacy tag names (`cli-verifiable`) per instruction — `LEGACY_TIER_MAP` maps them to `test-provable` at parse time.\n- Risk: Story may require zero code changes if previous stories already added all tests.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 17\n- By tool: Read: 7, Grep: 7, Glob: 3, Write: 1\n- Files read: 9 unique, 10 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n","numLines":18,"startLine":1,"totalLines":18}}}
